sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { ContainerMoviePrincipal, ContainerMovie } from './styled' import { useHistory } from 'react-router' import { goToMovie } from '../../routers/cordinator' const moviesOriginaisNetflix = (props) => { const history = useHistory() const onClickCard = (id) => goToMovie (history, id) return ( onClickCard()}> ) } export default moviesOriginaisNetflix
